title: 100 Disco Hits 5CD Best album set (musicfromrizzo)
description:
Hi folks, please check out all our tons of music uploads from this 
era we have previously posted here for you.

This offering here is called "100 Hits - the best Disco album"

There several nice songs on here, most of which we already have
in our previous postings here for you, however there's a new song
or two to add to your collection I'm sure. I enjoyed listening
a moment ago to "Jack and Jill" by Raydio - I remember listening
to this song a number of times decades ago and since - real nice
music I say! Then there's the beautifully done "I love music" by
the O'Jays , and "Got to be real" by Cheryl Lyn. "I love to love"
The Emotions with "Best of my love"  YMCA (village people)
Andrea True Connection with "More more more"
- then there's nice new finds like "Native New Yorker" among many
Disco standards included here such as "Boogie nights"
Of course there's Earth wind and fire with "September" and
Boogie wonderland" Vicki Sue Robinson with "Turn the beat around"
And to set the mood  for some , there's even Leo Sayer singing
"You make me feel like dancing" (not exactly disco, but certainly
70s music too)

No doubt some of the songs here are really simply "filler material" -
but then some folks cant get enough of this stuff from this era.

thanks for seeding our music torrents

Michael Rizzo Chessman
(musicfromrizzo)
